      "body" : "FWIW, I started (and I think did most of the hard parts?) this in my `qrcode` branch, but I don't intend to finish it now since I don't really have a way to test it... so if someone else wants to complete it, feel free (but mention here so we don't duplicate work)\r\n\r\n> Do other desktop wallets have that?\r\n\r\nAt least Electrum does.\r\n\r\n> How many people really want to scan a QR code on their desktop?\r\n\r\nThere's also no reason to assume Core is running only on a desktop...",
